channel.title: Web Client - Stuck on Starting Up
channel.description: Hello I've recently tried making a web client for my PI base HyBrid PvP source using this guide, [url=http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/tutorials/300270-how-make-webclient-hybrid-pvp-v2-client.html]HyBrid Pvp's owner made it..[/url], so i figured it should work but i followed it step by step and yet it still doesn't work. I've retryed it 5 times but every time it gets stuck on Starting Up, if you need any more info just let me know.. PLEASE HELP!
